<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="71" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">
Known from several localities in Yunnan Province (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Distribution of Polyalthopsis chinensis, P. floribunda and P. verrucipes." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.148.50929.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/413845" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">5</figureCitation>
): Hei-long-tan and Manxi in Meng-hai County and Kun-man in Meng-yang Town, Jinghong, growing in rain forests, at medium elevations (1300-1800 m a.s.l.).
</paragraph>
